      "role": "user",
      "content": "everything is just gone. i looked at my accounts today and i literally felt the floor drop out from under me. it's not even just the money, it's like... everything i worked for, everything i was supposed to be. it's all just zero. i feel like i'm just falling in this huge dark hole and there's no bottom.",
